annotations.comment: Labels:description: StorageOS transforms commodity server or cloud based disk capacity into     enterprise-class storage to run persistent workloads such as databases in containers.  Provides     high availability, low latency persistent block storage.  No other hardware or software is required.
Labels:io.k8s.description: The StorageOS Node container runs on all nodes that consume or provide storage
Labels:summary: Highly-available persistent block storage for containerized applications
